title: Whispered Words on a Beach
description:
Welcome to episode 87 of Sleep and Relax ASMR! Today's episode I'll be whispering various words and phrases over a calm beach recording. The episode includes both easy-to-understand and inaudible whispering. Enjoy!

Visit our website: www.SleepandRelaxASMR.com to get updates and access to special promos on awesome brands!
